Using block level button groups will allow the group to stretch the full width of the view port. This is useful for smaller viewports.

```jsx
<div className="grid gap-3">
  <ButtonGroup 
    look="hero" 
    block
    buttons={[
      { value: "Email", label: "Email"}, 
      { value: "Phone", label: "Phone" },
      { value: "SMS", label: "SMS" }
    ]}
  />
</div>
```
